{"tid":134416,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【食卡點算？】內地狂男徒手拆ATM機過程大曝光","createTime":"2017-02-25T12:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T02:47:36.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c9bc93f63086cd864404e54e03879365f060fd","tid":134416,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488024749_0edb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488024749_0edb.jpg&h=d551dec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170225/large/1488024890_8cff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170225%2Flarge%2F1488024890_8cff.jpg&h=acd7d098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名內地男子昨晚徒手拆開滙豐銀行ATM提款機事件，令不少網民譁然，《蘋果》獲得一批現場直擊相片，並聯絡到目擊者葉先生講述事件經過，他坦言對於該內地男子能徒手拆開櫃員機感到驚訝：「佢一隻腳頂住部機，然後就用手係咁扯！&hellip;&hellip;佢搖吓又停吓，搖咗5、6分鐘就搖開到條邊，之後仲拆埋部機！」<br />\n<br />\n目擊者葉先生昨晚在尖沙嘴碼頭附近拍照，其間見一名男子在滙豐銀行ATM內有所動作，遂轉移鏡頭，估不到拍攝到該男子的刑毀犯案過程。「當時見佢係咁搖部機，&hellip;&hellip;我有一刻喺度諗『佢係咪偷錢？會唔會見到我影相，搶我部手機㗎』。」葉先生遂不敢走近，只站在銀行外隔著玻璃拍攝，同時打電話報警。<br />\n<br />\n惟相隔5、6分鐘警員仍未到，他眼見該男子已徒手拆開櫃員機，「見佢一直望住個插卡位」，只好再報警。幸而警方隨即派員到場，「個男人(見到警察)成個人震晒！」葉先生其後得知，警方經初步調查後，證實該男子為內地旅客，因提款時被「食卡」，心急想取回提款卡就拆機。<br />\n<br />\n據知，警方事後在拆毀的櫃員機內，確實找到一張提款卡，相信是該名男子所有，惟事件涉及刑毀，最後將28歲姓廖的內地男子拘捕，並在其行李喼內發現大批精神科藥物。"},{"pid":"9ae8ef6ae94d46e4d49783e59f0521f44d794ebd","tid":134416,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d58a86a18ea99ca396c1b31ed76300b44be708b","tid":134416,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:58:41.000Z","msg":"中國奇人異事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3977eaeba8a77204d953a74f430c231dafd6ff","tid":134416,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T13:01:46.000Z","msg":"在其行李喼內發現大批精神科藥物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醒目喎"},{"pid":"42a7eec2ad0bf86f3988bf264de6c46dcc182a0e","tid":134416,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T02:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d1749c03268f83fe4ce0f117b77913b5b37895","tid":134416,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T02:38:03.000Z","msg":"內你老母"},{"pid":"f2c0c49dba204f3f06f858baeeef04974c0a340c","tid":134416,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T02:42:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在其行李喼內發現大批精神科藥物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醒目喎</blockquote><br />\n有藥唔洗坐？入青山同班精神病一齊坐"},{"pid":"fcccf4eb45d3214118be40287c6f6fe424cc009f","tid":134416,"uid":8751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T02:47:36.000Z","msg":"又有新院友"}]}